column3: Wow, look at the beautiful waves as they crash against the rock! I would love to see this in person someday in my travels.
Dirt bike riding as a sport is so brutish, no real skill involved like playing classical instruments
I would fight to get this car, it is the perfect car for me!
Why would anyone do this? What a horrible tragedy! Someone will pay for this!
